                <!-- Information -->
                ‘Welcome to the world wide web’ 


                <p></p> 
                In its simplest terms, HTML (hypertext markup language) was a coding language dedicated to organising specific information to be displayed on a web browser. While the 1st publically published version appeared in 1993, it technically existed long before that in the late 1980's. This language would contribute to the rapid expansion of the internet in the late 1990's/early 2000's. 
                <p></p>
                The first form of HTML was incredibly simple. The internet at this time was treated far more as a utilitarian tool rather than what it is today. 
                <p></p>

                HTML 1.0: 
                <p></p>
                <h4>Document structure</h4>
                    <pre>
                        &lt;HEAD> &lt;HTML> &lt;BODY> &lt;TITLE>
                    </pre>
                    <p></p>

                <p></p>
                <h4>Text formatting</h4>
                    <pre>
                        &lt;B> bold
                        &lt;I> italic
                        &lt;U> underline
                        &lt;EM> emphasis
                        &lt;STRONG>

                        &lt;CITE>
                        &lt;CODE>
                        &lt;KBD>
                        &lt;SAMP> 
                        &lt;DFN>
                        &lt;VAR>
                        &lt;TT>

                        Lists
                        &lt;UL>
                        &lt;UO>
                        &lt;LI>
                        &lt;DL>
                        &lt;DT> 
                        &lt;DD>
                        &lt;DIR>
                        &lt;MENU>

                        headings
                        &lt;H1> &lt;H2> &lt;H3> &lt;H4> &lt;H5> &lt;H6>

                        links and navigation
                        &lt;A>
                        &lt;BASE>
                        &lt;LINK>
                        &lt;NEXTID>
                        
                        &lt;BLOCKQUOTE>
                        
                        &lt;IMG>

                        &lt;ISINDEX>

                        &lt;ADDRESS>

                        &lt;PRE> 
                        &lt;PLAINTEXT>
                        &lt;LISTING> 
                        &lt;XMP>

                    </pre>
                <p></p>
                /headings
